reviewText: This is truly an inspirational set of DVD's I could watch over and over and not get tired of it.
Just as described.  Awesome.  Loved it!
One of the best film series regarding chefs and their craft. Purchased on their own prior.  Glad to have the whole set in one.

Nice presentation (i have not watched all DVDs yet) with a numbered box (limited edition).
The box reads "english-spanish" subtitles, but some of the individual dvd cases indicate only english subtitles. This was important for me since it is a french edition and I was giving it as a present for a native spanish speaker.
